{"title":"编席","authors":["张诚"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":6,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"编席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张诚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月的夜风温柔清凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们月下编席忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想着田里的小麦黄了梢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜悦的心情如春水荡漾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心情激荡，轻声歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双双巧手灵活紧张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银亮的苇眉子在手里飞舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锦缎似的席子在身后伸长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"席子上编织的花纹儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像是麦海起伏的波浪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"席子上编的丰收图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是公社社员的理想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银白的席子编好啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快送进新盖的粮仓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单等开镰的喜日到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把金色的麦粒往囤里装！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}